&lt;/span>
&lt;/h4>
&lt;p>$$x(t) = t^2 - 3, \quad y(t) = 2t + 1, \quad -2 \leq t \leq 3.$$&lt;/p></description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://buezw.github.io/docs/uoft/24/calculus/calculus10.parametricequationsandpolarcoordinates/feature.png"/></item></channel></rss>